[Changes for 0.04 - 2004-09-08]

* "Zero" is now supported, prompted by Chia-Liang Kao.

[Changes for 0.03 - 2002-11-23]

* Support for currency values, prompted by Dieter Simader.
* New module: Lingua::ZH::Numbers::Currency.

[Changes for 0.02 - 2002-10-30]

* Big5's digits was broken -- six got mixed with seven.
  (Thanks to Plasmaball for pointing out.)

[Changes for 0.02 - 2002-10-29]

* Initial release.
